{"tid":1945662,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵已將831兩站CCTV片段交予教大生代表律師","createTime":"2020-03-27T08:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T12:30:37.000Z","uid":134071,"like":304,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"c72b1d3f0cbdfaec1188f73d9fced4607112866c","tid":1945662,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:11:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200327/YIVGUKKAIIOG6EHU5J6EMYUBXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200327%2FYIVGUKKAIIOG6EHU5J6EMYUBXE%2F&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=17a82039\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200327%2FYIVGUKKAIIOG6EHU5J6EMYUBXE%2F&h=0bfd6dbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200327/YIVGUKKAIIOG6EHU5J6EMYUBXE/</a><br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】港鐵已將831兩站CCTV片段交予教大生代表律師<br />\n1小時前<br />\n<br />\n去年8.31警方在港鐵太子站搜捕示威者，其間涉嫌襲擊和拘禁無辜市民。教育大學學生會時任會長梁耀霆稱遭警員無理毆打和拘捕，早前向港鐵索取太子站和荔枝角站的閉路電視片段，擬用於民事控告警方，但遭港鐵拒絕。案件經審訊後，高等法院上周三下令港鐵須於七個工作天內交出該些關閉路電視片段。<strong>據了解，港鐵已將有關片段交予梁的代表律師。</strong>"},{"pid":"b3529c45df3c36bc48699861e54623f9f9efb120","tid":1945662,"uid":134071,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:11:59.000Z","msg":"<strong>梁耀霆向法庭承諾，只將片段用於法律行動，未經法庭許可不得擅自公開片段。</strong><br />\n<br />\n有關片段包括去年8月31日晚上10時40分至9月1日凌晨1時30分的太子站片段，及9月1日凌晨1時25分至2時的荔枝角站片段。梁於831當晚在太子站被捕，後來被押至荔枝角站並帶到警署，至今沒被起訴。"},{"pid":"f2ed52f243bedfd18d73f9c047034c94877b7628","tid":1945662,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63da4efe5c8db4a74d23821773ebaa21afc8d41","tid":1945662,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c065efd9e15b8acd32404bd08a452a46af3fc4b7","tid":