2F&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=17a82039\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200327%2FYIVGUKKAIIOG6EHU5J6EMYUBXE%2F&h=0bfd6dbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200327/YIVGUKKAIIOG6EHU5J6EMYUBXE/</a><br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】港鐵已將831兩站CCTV片段交予教大生代表律師<br />\n1小時前<br />\n<br />\n去年8.31警方在港鐵太子站搜捕示威者，其間涉嫌襲擊和拘禁無辜市民。教育大學學生會時任會長梁耀霆稱遭警員無理毆打和拘捕，早前向港鐵索取太子站和荔枝角站的閉路電視片段，擬用於民事控告警方，但遭港鐵拒絕。案件經審訊後，高等法院上周三下令港鐵須於七個工作天內交出該些關閉路電視片段。<strong>據了解，港鐵已將有關片段交予梁的代表律師。</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:59:53.000Z","msg":"樓主借個位黎置頂可以嗎<br />\n<br />\n要人要錢要資源！線下文宣全港大行動 重建文宣網絡<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fjiGAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fjiGAS</a>"},{"pid":"5a809434db6f394d77d75e5e59fa6c06760d4557","tid":1945662,"uid":155598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:11:44.000Z","msg":"狗鐵係咪需要向公眾交代下內容呢"},{"pid":"0b74e4f39c652f8b1b685103a202187923b6cec6","tid":1945662,"uid":68080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:15:29.000Z","msg":"查下條片真假之後俾美國同英國<br />\n兩邊都話要黑警證據<br />\n<br />\npin"},{"pid":"75fcddefbdaedc68c8cadba86a8ab691f58f3f38","tid":1945662,"uid":36531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:16:14.000Z","msg":"係要法院判先拎出黎<br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"12c616809f517d592b070ff5de66b7c9d8e69949","tid":1945662,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eba1bb57aafb927e74c2d6c0d1e0f108c206226d","tid":1945662,"uid":135274,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"f30f8693cbc0d0fcc61f608ebc0f25c5a417d00e","tid":1945662,"uid":95138,"like":55,"dislike":3,"score":52,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:13:29.000Z","msg":"又用據了解放風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實721有冇申請到CCTV?"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:15:08.000Z","msg":"如果有721受傷者希望向暴徒作民事訴訟，可以入稟要求港鐵披露閉路電視片段，法律理據同831太子站一樣，不過未有人做<b